  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 180°C (350°F).",
    "In a bowl, mix sweet potatoes with 1 tbsp olive oil and fresh herbs.",
    "Add caramelized sugar sauce to the sweet potatoes and mix well.",
    "Transfer to a baking dish and bake for 25 minutes until tender and caramelized.",
    "Let rest for 5 minutes before serving."
